metadata.name: MetaPlank#1
metadata.description: 3,000 MetaPlankz are here to remind you that you are never alone in this journey! MetaPlankz are unique and randomly generated 2D NFT. Some appear to be normal, and some appear to be sophisticated.  MetaPlankz believe in creating a unique environment and community, while combining the physical and digital worlds in a way that will enable all MetaPlankz to connect with each other, create strong friendships, and foster individual growth. We want to contribute in this new pioneering space by investing into metaverse real estate
